/* Rasberry Pi2 box (should fit B+ as well)
How it works:
    Make a rounded box
    Subtract the interior 
    Enlarge the devices so they protrude then subtract them.
    Slice top and bottom halves.
    Add lugs, holes and stand offs
*/

